{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_04_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 私って怖いんでしょうか？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私って怖いんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am I scary?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどうしたんだ？　何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's going on all of a sudden? Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それが……SNSに「一ノ瀬怜は性格がきつくて\n怒ると怖そう」って書かれていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… On social media‚ they wrote that \"\nRei Ichinose has a strict personality and looks scary when angry.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それくらいならたまに見かけるので\n気にしないようにしてるんですが、今回は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ I wouldn't pay much attention to something like that\nsince I occasionally come across such comments‚ but this time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "「サニピのメンバーも一ノ瀬怜を怖がって\nいつも気を遣っていそう」とまで書かれていて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They even wrote‚ \"Even the members of Sunny Peace seem\nto be cautious around Rei Ichinose and always have to be careful.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私ってそんなに怖そうに見えますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I really come off as that scary?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜はクールで気が強いイメージがあるから\nきつい印象を持たれやすいのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Rei has a cool and strong image‚ it's easy for people to perceive you as strict.\nMaybe that's why they have a harsh impression of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが思ってるほど私はクールじゃありません\n現に今もこうして気にしてるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not as cool as everyone thinks. In fact‚ I'm currently concerned about this.\nIt's not cool to be swayed by comments on social media‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かにSNSの書き込みを見て一喜一憂するのは\nクールとは言えないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's not exactly cool to be overjoyed\nor troubled by comments on social media.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "もう……何がおかしいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… What's so funny?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、クールな印象が強い怜も、素顔は\n些細なことで思い悩む可愛い女の子なんだと思ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's just that even though Rei have a cool image‚\nyou're a cute girl who worries about trivial things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "か、可愛くなんてありません！　可愛いっていうのは\nさくらや千紗みたいな子のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Cute? T-There's nothing cute about me!\nBeing cute is for girls like Sakura or Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "私はさくらみたいに天真爛漫に笑えないし\n千紗みたいに守りたくなる笑顔も出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't laugh innocently like Sakura‚\nnor can I make a smile that makes you want to protect like Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？　分かり辛いだけで\n怜にも可愛いところは沢山あると思うが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? Maybe it's just hard to see‚\nbut I think there are many cute aspects to Rei as well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……。{user}さんと話してると\n真面目に悩んでるのがバカらしく思えてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… When I talk with {user}‚\nI start to feel silly for taking things so seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それでいいんじゃないか？　ネットの書き込みも\nそんなに深刻に考えずに、気楽に聞き流せばいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's okay‚ isn't it? You don't have to think\ntoo deeply about internet comments. Just casually let them pass by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうですね……\nなんだか話を聞いてもらったら少し気が楽になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true…\nSomehow‚ I feel a bit relieved after talking to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "役に立てたのなら良かった\nこれからも困ったことがあればいつでも相談してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I could be of help‚ then I'm glad.\nIf you ever have any problems‚ feel free to consult with me anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "-Next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nやっぱり私って怖いんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nAm I still scary after all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　昨日は納得してなかったか？\n今度はどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Weren't you convinced yesterday?\nWhat's going on now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ダンスレッスン中の千紗と雫に\n強い口調でダメ出しをしてしまったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ during dance practice‚ I ended up giving\nChisa and Shizuku some harsh criticism.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "二人とももっと踊れるはずなのに\n現状で満足しているように見えて、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of them are capable of dancing better‚\nbut they seem satisfied with the current level‚ so I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "最初は普通のアドバイスだったんです\nでもだんだんヒートアップして口調がきつくなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ it was just normal advice‚\nbut as I got more heated‚ my tone became harsher…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "気付いた時には二人ともチワワみたいに\nブルブル震えて怯えていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before I realized it‚ both of them were\ntrembling and scared like Chihuahuas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "正論を言ってるだけで責めてるつもりはなかったのに\n……私ってそんなに怖いんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't mean to blame them‚ I was just speaking logically…\n…Am I really that scary?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "怜に叱られて二人が怯えるのはよくあることじゃないか\n多分、千紗と雫もそれほど気にしていないと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's common for Chisa and Shizuku to feel scared when scolded by Rei.\nI don't think Chisa and Shizuku are overly concerned about it either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "私がいつも怖がらせてるみたいに言わないで下さい\nそりゃあ今までも似たようなことはありましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't say it like I always scare people.\nSure‚ there have been similar situations in the past‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "今回は自分でも厳しく言い過ぎた気がして……\nなんとなく顔を合わせ辛いんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but this time‚ I feel like I went too far with my words…\nIt's a bit difficult to face them now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "今夜はライブバトルがあるので、それまでに\n二人とちゃんと話したいと思ってるんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have a live battle tonight‚\nso I want to talk to both of them properly before that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
